title: Yahoo Lifestyle
text: You may become more aware of the sneaky ways you sabotage your own success. Often you can see an external foe, but its harder to catch and dismantle your own habits that disrupt productivity. One common key feature of most self-damaging tactics is how you might refuse to fully embrace and enjoy what life offers. You could hold back on love, even for yourself. Be kind and compassionate to yourself in all you do, starting with how you spend your time. Beau Taplin wrote, Sharpen your mind. Soften your heart. Get Your Complete Cosmic Profile
